62
00:02:48,160 --> 00:02:49,160
but also static shots

63
00:02:49,540 --> 00:02:50,540
where I just place my
gimbal on a even surface

64
00:02:52,600 --> 00:02:53,600
to create a time-lapse video.

65
00:02:54,710 --> 00:02:55,710
Now, tip number two is to shoot handheld.

66
00:02:56,770 --> 00:02:57,770
Like I've mentioned,

67
00:02:57,603 --> 00:02:58,603
most shots made during my travel videos

68
00:03:00,010 --> 00:03:01,010
are shot handheld.

69
